  "title": "Principal Consultant",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Provide Level 1 & Level 2 DBA support for enterprise database environments, ensuring high availability and performance.</p></li><li><p>Administer and support Microsoft SQL Server and Oracle databases, including installation, configuration, monitoring, and troubleshooting.</p></li><li><p>Possess working knowledge of MySQL for basic administration and support activities.</p></li><li><p>Perform daily BAU database health checks, backups, performance tuning, and database patching activities.</p></li><li><p>Support audit requirements, compliance checks, and coordinate with database vendors for issue resolution and upgrades.</p></li></ul>",
